OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but cloud will increase
OL,9,Flater to bring the odd shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,12,Fwith some hazy sunshine at times but
OL,13,Fthe odd shower is possible. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCooler
OL,16,Fand cloudy over the weekend with a
OL,17,Fchance of showers, these most
OL,18,Fwidespread on Saturday. Showery rain
OL,19,Fspreading southeast on Monday.
